    "body": "## Problem\r\n`vim.lsp.document_color.color_presentation()` throws, due to incorrect use of the `vim.Range` API.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nChange `vim.Range.has(a, b)` call to `a:has(b)`.",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-19T17:00:46Z",
